test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 0 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a03bdacebc0>([-1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a03bdacebc0> = [[-1], [-1], [-1]].count
 +  and   0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a03bdacebc0>([1, -1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7a03bdacebc0> = [[-1], [-1], [-1]].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 1 == -1
 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([-1, -1])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
